        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Access</strong> You're an aristocrat or honored retainer from a Chelaxian noble house.</p><hr /><p>A noble house has invested in your training, imparting special techniques the family has honed over generations. You gain @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Additional Lore] as a skill feat, choosing from among Cheliax Lore, Devil Lore, Hell Lore, or a Lore associated with your house. In addition, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Deception checks, Diplomacy checks, Intimidation checks, and your Will DC against Chelaxian citizens and devils.</p>"
